cell("markdown","# Math 07: Calculus — Differential Equations\n\n**Learning Objectives:**\n1. Solve separable differential equations analytically\n2. Visualize differential equations using Slope Fields\n3. Implement Euler's Method to approximate solutions computationally\n\n**Prerequisites:** Math 02 (Derivatives)\n**Estimated time:** 90 minutes\n**Textbook:** *Justin Skycak — Calculus* §3.1-3.2"),
